#####  General modification  #####

1. Change appearance
@Super-> Appearance :
	-> Look : Theme(Radiance)
	-> Behavior : auto hide launcher
@Super -> User Accounts : change headimage

2. Dowload "Chrome", "Gvim", "Adobe Flash Plugin", Delete "Bluetooth Management"
@Super-> Software Center
@ Chrome synchronization

3. Change some shortcuts
@Super-> keyboard -> Shorcuts :
	Disble "Alt" for UHD
	"Alt + Q" for close window
	"Alt + W" for maximize window(toggle)
	"Alt + E" for move window
	"Alt + R" for minimize window

4. Delete useless folders
: keep "Backup", "Config", "Desktop", "Documents", "Downloads"

5. Enable Pinyin input method
@Super -> Keyboard Input Method -> Input Method : add "Chinese Pinyin"
@Super -> Language Support -> Keyboard input method system : "ibus"

6. Add printer
@Super -> Printing -> Add -> Network Printer -> Find Network Printer : 128.205.35.56

7. Swap "Ctrl" and "CapLock"
@Super -> Keyboard Layout -> option.. -> Ctrl key position -> Swap Ctrl and CapsLock 

8. Termianl setting
@Super -> Terminal :
	Edit -> Keyboard Shortcuts : 
		disable menu access keys
		disable the menu shortcut key
	
	Edit -> Profile Preferences
		-> General : Font(Ubuntu Mono Bold Italic, 15)
		-> Color : Background(White)
		-> Background : Transparent background 
		-> Scrolling : Scrolling back(ulimited)

9. Install Dropbox
$ {
cd ~ && wget -O - "https://www.dropbox.com/download?plat=lnx.x86" | tar xzf -
~/.dropbox-dist/dropboxd
}

10. Setup git
$ {
ssh-keygen -t rsa
cd ~/.ssh
sudo apt-get install xclip
xclip -sel clip < ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
}
@ add SSH key to github

11. Apply other config
$ {
~/Config/Bin/vapply
}

12. Startup items
@Super -> Startup Applications :
	Dropbox : /home/xiaov/.dropbox-dist/dropboxd
	Terminal : gnome-terminal --maximize
$ {
sudo reboot
}


